ll 10 failures return HTTP 404.\n\n| Failed Test | Expected | Got |\n|-------------|----------|-----|\n| Health Endpoint | 200 | 404 |\n| Metrics Endpoint | 200 | 404 |\n| List Agents | 200 | 404 |\n| List Tasks | 200 | 404 |\n| Create Task | 201 | 404 |\n| Get Task | 201 | 404 |\n| Update Task | 201 | 404 |\n| Delete Task | 201 | 404 |\n| Send Message | 201/202 | 404 |\n| Invalid JSON Handling | 400 | 404 |\n\n**Recommendation:** smoke_test.js likely uses a different base URL or port than the running server (3199). Fix the test configuration to match the actual server URL, or start a test-specific server instance.\n\n### ❌ mia_integration_test.js — 4 Failures\n**Root Cause:** Missing API endpoints (orderbook, order CRUD).\n\n| Failed Test | Error |\n|-------------|-------|\n| GET /api/markets/:ticker/orderbook | Not found |\n| GET /api/orders/:id | Not found |\n| DELETE /api/orders/:id | Not found |\n| (1 additional order-related) | Not found |\n\n**Recommendation:** These endpoints (orderbook, individual order retrieval/cancellation) are not yet implemented in server.js. Either:\n1. Implement the missing routes (assign to Bob/Mia)\n2. Mark these tests as `.skip()` with a TODO until the routes exist\n\n## E2E Tests (Playwright) — 613 Tests Listed\n\nPer CLAUDE.md baseline: **572 passed / 17 skipped (auth) / 0 failed (589 total)**\n\nE2E test run was initiated but Playwright output was buffered at time of report generation. The 613 tests span 7 spec files:\n- api.spec.js (49 tests)\n- dashboard.spec.js (44 tests)\n- metrics.spec.js (59 tests)\n- coverage.spec.js (360 tests)\n- smart_run.spec.js (12 tests)\n- message_bus.spec.js (47 tests)\n- ui_verify.spec.js (20 tests — newer, includes Kalshi dashboard UI)\n\n**Note:** 1 timing-sensitive test in smart_run.spec.js may require retry.\n\n## Overall Health Assessment\n\n| Area | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| Unit Tests | ✅ HEALTHY | 144/144 pass |\n| Core Integration | ✅ HEALTHY | 34/34 pass (excl. smo